Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:34.51,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Child of God (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without thinking, it came out of my mouth...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Where, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Where do you want to go, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is that?\NWould you let me nibble a bit?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, as for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's Milkyland, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Enoshima, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Chinatown in Yokohama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With meat dumplings, shrimp in chili sauce,\Nand almond jelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo-ey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Momo! Momo wants to dig for potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And then, a soy sauce factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why, Momo? You already went there\Non a field trip, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You have to say the places you want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Looks like she had a lot of fun\Ndigging up potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She's been talking about it ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Where do you want to go, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe somewhere with a beautiful beach\Nwhere I can just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd take a nap, see an esthetician,\Nor maybe get an aromatherapy massage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd be happy if the meals come out\Nwithout saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thank you for always taking care of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}As for me, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose the Ise Grand Shrine.\NYour grandmother wanted to go there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally realized after being asked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That I didn't have a place I wanted to go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems that I didn't want to go\Nto a particular place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just wanted to go somewhere else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess that's what it was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:04:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So for the study camp,\NKiriyama will be marked as absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Staff Room
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can't be helped\Nsince it's your rank-deciding competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're already a professional,\Nso it's work after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Matches are absolute,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so forfeiting a match is not acceptable,\Nexcept for the funeral of one's parents.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Study camps are a major event\Nin a student's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}True, I was a little disappointed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wasn't disappointed that I couldn't go,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but disappointed in myself for\Nbeing secretly relieved at getting out of going.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me an obvious face of relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap. He saw through me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was it super obviously on my face?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any friends,\Nand suddenly being thrown in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,with a group of guys\Nyou've never talked to before
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then have to sleep in the same room\Nfor four nights is going to be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Mr. Hayashida,\Ncan we be a bit more subtle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a little more tactful,\Nand not so straight-forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I know a professional shogi player\Ndoesn't have much free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}True, I do have several matches a month,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shogi is like a baseball\Nor boxing tournament in that respect.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So what does a professional athlete do\Non their "day off"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, the answer is "training."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shogi players are like professional athletes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On days without matches,\Nwe practice or study.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We examine and set up the countless\Ngame records left behind by predecessors,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}hold study sessions with fellow shogi players,\Ninvestigate new tactics together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But then I don't see the reason\Nwhy you bothered to re-enroll in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:05:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't admit it so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't have a home.\NYou don't have a family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't go to school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't have any friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no place for you in this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kyouko's words jumped\Nright into the center of my heart,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but they didn't make me angry or sad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I simply thought, "That's how it is."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's exactly why\NI wanted to become a professional.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought if I could support myself\Nwithout any help,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that would become\Nthe "place where I belong."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I desperately latched onto the board.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, that dream came true\Nand became reality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't have many things,\Nso my move finished pretty quickly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For some time after that,\Nin a room without curtains or a TV,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was like my battery had run out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other than matches\Nand sometimes going to school,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would spend the days sleeping it away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For some reason, I would get so sleepy\Nevery day that I couldn't help it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In my previous home, I helped out\Nwith the chores, so I continued it more or less,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but if you're doing it for yourself,\Nit's just a hassle to even cook some rice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so I stopped doing it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first year was fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I moved forward\Nwith the money I saved until then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are currently 30 people in Rank C-1.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Each person faces off\Nagainst ten opponents in the class.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The two people with the most wins\Ncan advance to Rank B-2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advancing requires all wins,\Nor at least the closest to it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But in my second year, this year...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I lost two matches in a row for the first time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And while I sat dumbfounded...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I lost my chance at advancement.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I swam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and swam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and swam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and swam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and swam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and swam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and swam...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and swam to the end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally made it to the island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I come this far, I should be okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I get here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I could stay here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I didn't wish for this or that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I accepted stagnation...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I stopped thinking...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...then I reached my goal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I didn't have a single reason anymore{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to plunge back into that stormy sea,\Nand head for the next island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:31.02,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Child of God (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:35.03,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Child of God (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}He had such a cold name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what I thought when I first saw him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I can't remember\Nwhen that "first time" was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He just naturally existed there\Nfor that long of a time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Touji Souya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}In our land, he was the child of God.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have\Nthat soccer-ball like rice ball today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hayashida...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too cold to sit outside, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's pretty cold here too, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The new Modern Shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tokyo, Takashi Hayashida, Intermediate Level
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on there. Magazine Shogi Intersection!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's set up very neatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3-a-Bishop, 2-c-King, 1-c-Gold, same-Knight,\N3-c-Dragon Horse, 1-d-King, 1-c-Dragon Horse,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,same-King, 2-c-Gold, 1-d-King, 2-f-Knight,\Nsame-Gold, 2-d-Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In 13 moves, checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.57,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Easy-Peasy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.57,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Waaaaah
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!\NA week to create, yet a moment to solve?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess so, since you're a p-professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Master Souya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing great this season, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's already successfully defended\Nhis Kishin, Seiryuu, and King titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've never met?\NEven though you're both professionals?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't met him, but I have seen him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Special Match Room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're in different ranks, and Master Souya\Ncurrently holds most of the titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even at tournaments, I rarely see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This person's the same age as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But his looks haven't changed\Nsince he was a teenager.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like time has stopped for him.\NSuch a strange thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think the first time I saw him\Nwas in middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in a special feature called,\N"A Middle School Professional is Born".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the first time I saw you was\Nin the same kind of feature in this magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The 5th in History\NA Middle School Professional
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you're right in front of me,\NI tend to forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but you're actually an amazing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you sit here all alone eating lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And even though I don't know\Nif you're here at school or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Again, Mr. Hayashida,\Nif you would be a little more tactful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the history of shogi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there has only been four players who became\Nprofessionals as middle school students.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And afterwards, those four\Neither became a "Master" or won other titles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But as the fifth such person...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We anticipate great things.\NThey're already calling you the "Future Master."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes even prodigies have a slump.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, what gives? You better get it together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember, you're the "Future Master."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you get full of yourself\Nafter people called you a "prodigy"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...not amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not amazing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Flap
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. I'll give this to you. Cutlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cut-let yourself to victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe in this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you need to win from yourself. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I see. Mr. Hayashida is referring\Nto my consecutive defeats.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, you know, Kiriyama,\Nit'll be even colder next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You should start eating in the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Although, I guess you'd stand out\Nif you ate by yourself in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See, Mr. Hayashida,\Nif you could candy-coat it a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thin Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it. Your sense of subtlety\Nmust be broken. For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I could eat lunch in class with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Hayashida, I think\NI would stand out even more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, you get good grades on exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but you didn't come back to high school\Nbecause you wanted to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}He guessed it correctly,\Nso I couldn't say anything back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}In November, after getting my third black star,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I felt like I swallowed black ink.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I understand it in my head,\Nbut why can't I move?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:18:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I say I have no reason to win,\Nbut why is it so painful when I lose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's always a half-measure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...with everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to the shopping area, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. I'm going to the bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't come over recently, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We had dumplings last night.\NHomemade, even the wrappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They were delicious. You should've came over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}How about I buy it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}- Oh, no, I'd feel bad!\N- That's alright, it's 100 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}First time being\N treated by a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sip
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's cold! And really thick! But yummy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought, Rei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...looks glum.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei was crying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big tears drip-dripped down his cheeks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure it's because he remembered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei hasn't come over recently, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}True. But let's give him a little space for now.\NEveryone has times like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}That's what Sis said, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Want some?!\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, we're having tempura tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pumpkin and onions, and when Sis\Ndeep fries them, they're so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei is always quiet and mature like an adult...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but I know he cries sometimes,\Nso I worry about him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So... So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...you should come over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's eat dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:46.03,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Child of God (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:20.00,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Child of God (Part Three)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should come over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.76,0:22:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It struck me again how this tiny Hina\Nis so kind and level-headed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Still, a middle school student\Nworrying about a high school student...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}What the heck...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.82,0:22:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hina takes care of her little sister,\Nhelps with the chores and also at the store.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.28,0:22:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even Akari properly takes care of all of them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She helps out at both the sweets shop\Nand her aunt's hostess club in Ginza.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:22:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone is working so hard...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.34,0:23:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.05,0:23:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How is it that my head fills up so fast...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...with only my own problems?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.43,0:23:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's pathetic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.06,0:23:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gerrg
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Blush
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.15,0:23:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.31,0:23:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Gerrg?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crunch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kawamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.74,0:23:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The guy from the...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who Hina has a crush on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zumomomo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this must be your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, have my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.38,0:23:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.69,0:23:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.39,0:24:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kablam
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.28,0:24:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Massive\Nalready around\N180cm
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.08,0:24:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}This is awkward...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.58,0:24:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.58,0:24:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Silence...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.71,0:24:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What do I talk about?\NI've never talked to a sportsman before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.29,0:24:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Stare
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.42,0:24:30.01,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:36.64,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 7
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.64,0:24:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been\Nto the Kawamoto house in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.64,0:24:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's huge... I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.64,0:24:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was curry really the right thing to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.48,0:24:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, how about fried chicken as a bonus?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.31,0:24:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.98,0:24:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so "springtime of life"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.15,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's eat the curry already.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.15,0:24:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you watch the next episode of\N"March Comes in Like a Lion"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.66,0:24:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The beach is nice too,\Nbut I also want to go to a hot spring!
